00:23:36.980 --> 00:23:40.810
It cuts across all 13 disciplines,
and they learn basic

00:23:40.810 --> 00:23:41.860
things for the full year.

00:23:42.200 --> 00:23:45.050
They're learning things like
basic fundamental graphic skills,

00:23:45.160 --> 00:23:46.980
3D motion, and web applications.

00:23:46.980 --> 00:23:49.310
This obviously is not
a first-year project,

00:23:49.310 --> 00:23:51.980
but this student was once
a first-year student.

00:23:51.980 --> 00:23:52.980
Other curricular changes.

00:23:52.980 --> 00:23:56.780
In architecture,
we teach this immersion studio.

00:23:56.780 --> 00:24:00.780
