in density that you can achieve

00:46:43.590 --> 00:46:48.400
in a data center or in compute
in the same physical volume.

00:46:48.920 --> 00:46:50.860
It's a very high bandwidth
server architecture.

00:46:50.860 --> 00:46:55.030
We focused a lot of time and
effort making sure this thing can

