So we have 21.3 gigabytes a
second of processor bandwidth

00:47:03.070 --> 00:47:05.240
to those two processors.

00:47:05.260 --> 00:47:09.750
We have a 256-bit wide,
667 megahertz memory system.

00:47:09.750 --> 00:47:13.030
Again, very, very well balanced,
21 gigabytes a second of

00:47:13.030 --> 00:47:14.500
main memory bandwidth.

